				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/%E1%BA%A8m-t%E1%BB%ADu-k%E1%BB%B3-09/poem-vh1buZaMUlyu7rzCwNAkAw">Ẩm tửu kỳ 09 - 飲酒其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-CrRxrmDiaeNj-dOcA3Mp7g">Đông quân - 東君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-Di%E1%BB%85n/H%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BA%ABn-h%E1%BB%AFu-l%E1%BB%85-t%E1%BB%AB-chi-th%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%AD-c%E1%BB%AD-L%E1%BB%A5c-Gi%E1%BA%A3-s%E1%BB%B1-v%E1%BB%89-v%E1%BB%89-mi%E1%BB%85n-th%E1%BB%A5-t%E1%BA%A1-k%E1%BB%B7-d%C4%A9-thi/poem-mIHiOpfatHb6IEP1OSM2wA">Hành tẫn hữu lễ từ chi, thế tử cử Lục Giả sự vỉ vỉ miễn thụ, tạ kỷ dĩ thi - 行贐有禮辭之世子舉陸賈事亹亹勉受謝紀以詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-Di%E1%BB%85n/author-yjRlicU3gV4B06v3YivzTw">Lý Tư Diễn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-ng%C5%A9-th%E1%BB%A7-III-k%E1%BB%B3-1-Thi%C3%AAn-d%E1%BB%A5ng-m%E1%BA%A1c-nh%C6%B0-long/poem-e_vjcW03ocbPKgdXl4rrEg">Khiển hứng ngũ thủ (III) kỳ 1 (Thiên dụng mạc như long) - 遣興五首其一（天用莫如龍）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ph%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-M%C3%A3-song-ph%C3%A0m/poem-E-b4J2D8sMTFN6bgQnxwiQ">Lương Mã song phàm - 梁馬雙帆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ph%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m/author-kjKBPKP3VM3yjyBJUH1Xkw">Ngô Phúc Lâm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/M%E1%BB%99c-Lan-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-6sfuvKunKe6MYqxIDetwJA">Mộc Lan từ - 木蘭詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-B%E1%BA%A1ch-M%C3%A3-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C6%B0u/poem-dW9R6UpAsABiUgZsSbvYjA">Tặng Bạch Mã vương Bưu - 贈白馬王彪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-C%E1%BB%91-b%C3%A1t-ph%C3%A2n-v%C4%83n-h%E1%BB%8Dc-th%C3%ADch-H%E1%BB%93ng-C%C3%A1t-ch%C3%A2u/poem-HrYvDephDpfYnIZl-V2i2g">Tống Cố bát phân văn học thích Hồng Cát châu - 送顧八分文學適洪吉州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%E1%BB%A9-thi%E1%BA%BFt-1/poem-1bzkHrZqz1OlRdsFmQZd5A">Tứ thiết 1 - 駟驖 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
